snippet.title: These Doomed Isles Release Date Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
These Doomed Isles is coming to Steam Early Access on the 25th of September! 

You can wishlist the game here to get notified when it launches: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1840710/These_Doomed_Isles/

You can also join our Discord here to get involved in the discussion: https://discord.gg/FQuxCvmeUy
